Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures.properties

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.structures.properties
This package contains classes that represent properties of structures.

These properties can be used to add additional information to structures, such as their animation speed or how they handle redstone signals.

Each structure type should have its own set of properties that it supports. The values of these properties can be set per structure.
